# Synopsis

Billy recalls a traumatic event in front of a courtroom detailing a particular summer spent in the woods of (somewhere)
with Marcus - His younger brother.

# Characters

Mr Rymer     - Father
Mrs Rymer    - Mother
Billy Rymer  - Older brother
Marcus Rymer - Younger brother
Judge        - Judge
Ms Williams  - The teacher held accountable

# Chapters

1. Child's statement at court testifying against Ms Williams
2. Billy's statement at court testifying against the man
3. First day on their own


